From the balance sheet:
- Paid-in Capital initial amount: 13000000.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
- Paid-in Capital end amount: 13000000.00 (as of 2024-02-01)

The value remained the same during this period, indicating there were no additional capital contributions or returns of capital to shareholders during this time.
